title: Is IshowSpeed coming to India? YouTuber promises 2026 return after Payal Gaming S8UL Mumbai invite
summary_full: Darren Jason Watkins Jr., known as IShowSpeed, has promised to return to India in 2026 after Payal “Payal Gaming” Dhare invited him to visit the S8UL gaming house in Mumbai during his February 25 livestream. Speed last visited India in October 2023 during the ICC Men’s ODI World Cup, where his streams and meeting with Daler Mehndi went viral.
